{"tid":1544591,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我屌曬你地老母 唔好再自殺","createTime":"2019-09-05T15:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T06:21:53.000Z","uid":60562,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66c1396f311435134719d076540728464868d469","tid":1544591,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"我地仲有好多人同你一齊撐緊呀<br />\n係咪大家都放棄大家一齊死呀<br />\n多你一個好多 小你一個好小呀<br />\n你係咪想我地成班手足傷心死呀<br />\n<br />\n呢個政權唔會為左你既死有任何動搖架<br />\n以前d學生跳樓都無理過佢地呀<br />\n<br />\n我地要一齊光復香港呀<br />\n好快做到架啦 <br />\n好快成功架啦<br />\n<br />\n我愛你地 我地一齊唔好放棄好嗎"},{"pid":"c5a428a7cf2f07d928a2cf82de661d5a28f2d0d5","tid":1544591,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45b22665b5cc36fa57bfd1494f400a6b8927f2a1","tid":1544591,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"我地就黎成功架啦"},{"pid":"a6048eb1766f412ef42450883d4030860c4cb0ed","tid":1544591,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:19:40.000Z","msg":"----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n太子CCTV最快星期6會被刪除<br />\n我地要有一次大集氣出太子 制造輿論壓力<br />\n將831死人嘅概念植入市民心中<br />\n令全港市民聚焦落黨鐵 迫佢交831嘅CCTV<br />\n絕對唔係要依兩日咁得幾十人圍太子警署咁<br />\n一定要上千人<br />\n實行將太子站鋪滿白色鮮花<br />\n<br />\n若然屬實 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日就係手足頭七</span></span><br />\n依家號召各位巴打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花</span></span><br />\n見字嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">巴打幫手spread出去</span></span> 一個人真係推唔起<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【831】9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花行動post<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544326</a>"},{"pid":"5bfa72bf108815d9c0613a86eecf3bb323929c3d","tid":1544591,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"贏就一齊贏，輸咪一齊面對<br />\n我地一齊堅持落去好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔準再離隊呀，我要煲底見，頂唔順咪約出黎等你攬下我囉，我好好攬㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14beb04ed6a113129588b93bb86eaae3f4d3ec45","tid":1544591,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"bd8909e8ae09b69215931f1bd5d75503bca6b75c","tid":1544591,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bfa72bf108815d9c0613a86eecf3bb323929c3d","tid":1544591,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"贏就一齊贏，輸咪一齊面對<br />\n我地一齊堅持落去好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔準再離隊呀，我要煲底見，頂唔順咪約出黎等你攬下我囉，我好好攬㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"一齊大擁抱"},{"pid":"238abff4dccece0a5231b8bda67866a444f18baa","tid":1544591,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"大家都好努力<br />\n好似攬炒巴咁講：只要大家一日唔放棄 我都唔會放棄<br />\n我地話過有一日會係煲底除罩相擁<br />\n時間會過去的，我地有一日會見證到呢一刻<br />\n只要依家呢一刻既你願意堅持落去！<br />\n<br />\n香港需要每一個香港人既力量！<br />\n最重要係唔可以冇左你既力量！<br />\n因為冇人係可以代替到你既位置！<br />\n一齊捱落去，就會見到成果！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de30f2e455